<ol><li>
Access from the R project: source the file at <a href="api/R">api/R</a>
<li>Access using simple http links: use wizard at <a href="api/find">api/find</a>
<li>Access using web services: use this <a href="api/soap?wsdl">WSDL file</a>
</ol>

<#--end of your plugin-->	
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</form>
</#macro>
